Class Apriori.RuleGeneratorBuilder<ItemType extends Item>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mrapp.apriori.Apriori.RuleGeneratorBuilder<ItemType>
  • Type Parameters:
    ItemType - The type of the items, which are processed by the algorithm
    Enclosing class:
    Apriori<ItemType extends Item>

    public static class Apriori.RuleGeneratorBuilder<ItemType extends Item>
extends java.lang.Object
    A builder, which allows to configure and create instances of the class Apriori, which are configured to generate association rules.
